reviewText: Excellent Product.  Arrived in a timely fashion.  Top Quality.
Was for my mother-in-law.  She loves these old shows.
Very funny show my Mom loves it.

An enjoyable series of a time gone by. Hoping a 4th release comes out as there are quite a few episodes that were on the video release many years ago not yet been transferred to DVD. Only disspointed that a bit more thought hadn't gone into releasing the episodes in chronological order of the airdates and a little bit of restoration...
Somewhat similar to situations Lucy would get into but a bit more classy. I have enjoyed these immensely

I have been a fan of Joan Davis for so many years. Love her comedy. I grew up watching her in many movies - my favorite was Hold That Ghost with Abbott and Costello. The combination of these three great comedians was the ultimate comedic enjoyment. I am so happy with the I Married Joan collection I purchased from Amazon.
